OL,3,CUK pension age review must recognise
OL,4,CScotland's demographics, says
OL,5,CSomerville
OL,7,FAn ongoing review of the pension age
OL,8,Fin the UK must recognise Scotland's
OL,9,Fdemographics, the country's Social
OL,10,FJustice Secretary has said.
OL,12,FA regular review of the State Pension
OL,13,Fage was opened earlier this year by
OL,14,Fthe UK Government, with the Scottish
OL,15,FGovernment submitting its views for
OL,16,Fany changes.
