OL,3,CUK pension age review must recognise
OL,4,CScotland's demographics, says
OL,5,CSomerville
OL,7,FIn her submission, Social Justice
OL,8,FSecretary Shirley-Anne Somerville said
OL,9,Flower life expectancy in Scotland than
OL,10,Felsewhere in the UK risks inequalities
OL,11,Fin pensions.
OL,13,F"Here in Scotland, both men and women
OL,14,Fhave a lower average life expectancy
OL,15,Fat the current State Pension age of
OL,16,F66," she said.
