OL,3,CUK pension age review must recognise
OL,4,CScotland's demographics, says
OL,5,CSomerville
OL,7,F"Inequalities in life expectancy,
OL,8,Fincluding healthy life expectancy,
OL,9,Fwithin the population are significant
OL,10,Fin Scotland, and reducing poverty and
OL,11,Finequality therefore remains the best
OL,12,Fway of improving life expectancy.
OL,14,F"Nonetheless, it is important that
OL,15,Fcurrent variations in life expectancy
OL,16,Fare highlighted in your review to
OL,17,Fensure that any potential changes do
OL,18,Fnot penalise those who have made
OL,19,Fsimilar contributions over the course
OL,20,Fof their lives.
