OL,3,CUK pension age review must recognise
OL,4,CScotland's demographics, says
OL,5,CSomerville
OL,7,F"Pensions inequalities mean that
OL,8,Fwomen, people with multiple low pay
OL,9,Fjobs, disabled people, minority ethnic
OL,10,Fcommunities and people who are self-
OL,11,Femployed, all face lower pension
OL,12,Fincomes in retirement."
OL,14,FWhile the Scottish Government is
OL,15,F"doing everything within our powers"
OL,16,Fto tackle poverty, Ms Somerville
OL,17,Fadded: "The Scottish Government does
OL,18,Fnot want to see any changes that do
OL,19,Fnot fundamentally consider Scotland's
OL,20,Funique challenges."
