OL,3,CUK pension age review must recognise
OL,4,CScotland's demographics, says
OL,5,CSomerville
OL,7,FMs Somerville also urged the
OL,8,FGovernment to offer compensation to
OL,9,Fthe Waspi (Women Against State Pension
OL,10,FInequality) women ` who were born in
OL,11,Fthe 1950s and not adequately informed
OL,12,Fabout a change to the State Pension
OL,13,Fage.
OL,15,FA compensation scheme has previously
OL,16,Fbeen ruled out by the UK Government,
OL,17,Fwith costs estimated at about #10.5
OL,18,Fbillion.
