OL,3,CUK pension age review must recognise
OL,4,CScotland's demographics, says
OL,5,CSomerville
OL,7,F"Further, any review of the state
OL,8,Fpension age must address previous
OL,9,Fmistakes and ensure justice for women
OL,10,Fborn in the 1950s," Ms Somerville said.
OL,12,F"Although the UK Government
OL,13,Facknowledged their mishandling of
OL,14,Fthis, there has yet to be any
OL,15,Fcompensation paid to the Waspi women
OL,16,Fdespite pressure from both
OL,17,Fstakeholders and the Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment.
